{"tid":2237311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"假疫苗案 官拒律政司申董事撤控","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T07:24:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b8fcf001929fd2482a99eab66ba4cfa8788435cf","tid":2237311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/HRMIYRXPIRCUDJITTRQGC5NH3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FHRMIYRXPIRCUDJITTRQGC5NH3A%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=53ff8229\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FHRMIYRXPIRCUDJITTRQGC5NH3A%2F&h=03c517cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/HRMIYRXPIRCUDJITTRQGC5NH3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n假疫苗案 官拒律政司申董事撤控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VSReBtlmarZ_2djvDbfdSmD4VFg=/708x398/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QVRD7NUKJFDU5LPA7D5IP6HRVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVSReBtlmarZ_2djvDbfdSmD4VFg%3D%2F708x398%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQVRD7NUKJFDU5LPA7D5IP6HRVI.jpg&h=d71005d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官錢禮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】衞生署及海關去年7月11日聯合巡查銅鑼灣一家醫療集團，撿取一批子宮頸癌疫苗後，驗出其中六支是冒牌貨。涉事公司昨在東區法院承認違反《商品說明條例》，公司董事則獲控方撤控。惟主任裁判官錢禮直言案情嚴重，涉及嚴重公眾健康議題，一支疫苗亦不應有問題，董事卻不用為此負責，明言不能接受如此處理案件。裁判官最終沒接納撤控，並將案件押後至11月13日再訊，屆時控方須就撤控做法提供詳盡解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注射後死亡風險增<br />\n<br />\n涉案的港健醫療集團有限公司被票控一項「管有已應用虛假商品說明的貨品作售賣或任何商業或製造用途」罪，即聲稱涉案假疫苗由藥廠MSC製造。公司代表昨認罪，女董事張維瑄（55歲）亦被控同罪，昨獲控方申請撤控。<br />\n<br />\n惟裁判官指出，本案涉及嚴重公共健康議題，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近年本港不時揭發假疫苗，去年7月海關與衞生署接獲市民舉報後，突擊搜查位於觀塘的信穎醫務中心時，撿獲76盒冒牌子宮頸癌疫苗，約值17.4萬元。涉案董事楊文信（52歲）承認一項售賣偽造商標貨品罪，今年6月被署理主任裁判官徐綺薇判監四個月，獲准保釋等候上訴。該醫務中心的則被控管有偽造商標貨品罪，遭罰款兩萬元。<br />\n<br />\n徐官判刑時指，楊身為醫生，卻未有合理及謹慎地處理受監管藥物，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1352、ESS12079/20"},{"pid":"06ae419871e69fb8b5f747db6f93a214abdc4854","tid":2237311,"uid":123738,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"係用黎昆支那狗同藍屍廢老架，律政屍出埋手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7a705c0a4307d79f1ea827b80175b315b7b61c","tid":2237311,"uid":188282,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"吓?<br />\n咁如果11月律政個解釋冇說服力，係繼續叫佢無限解釋?"},{"pid":"ad3970136e87ddd2d39d05f65706a2aeda2de952","tid":2237311,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"政權同商人千絲萬縷勾結<br />\n死都唔告，法庭吹得漲咩？<br />\n<br />\n立法機關都唔做野"},{"pid":"40d50a9719a3a285721263854d3dbb4fd9982d36","tid":2237311,"uid":153811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cf45927f3940ff05c4e8c0986a6ade5f8c730d","tid":2237311,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思幫我入嚟睇睇好嗎<br />\n[警世post] 終結失敗循環 面對獨裁絕不妥協<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c7b184d04a96c611d328bbd897350a3c85a720b","tid":2237311,"uid":153811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40d50a9719a3a285721263854d3dbb4fd9982d36","tid":2237311,"uid":153811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a246c6b562564ca1737593c8258ca7e0533796","tid":2237311,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40d50a9719a3a285721263854d3dbb4fd9982d36",